Days after Baba Siddique's murder, the Bollywood actor Salman Khan is under radar amid new death threats. The actor's safety and security became a major cause of concern after the NCP leader and Salman Khan's friend was shot outside son Zeeshan Siddique’s office in Mumbai's Neelamnagar on October 12 night by three armed men.
